AddressInfo.Title: Briar Chapel /  15-501 Shopping Center
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Small shopping area outside of Briar Chapel, conveniently accessed from 15-501. Look for Breakaway Cafe, Town Hall Burger and Beer, Alberello Cafe, etc.

GeneralComments: Free charging station located in middle of parking lot outside Breakway Cafe, Town Hall Burger and Beer, Alberello Cafe, etc. Two J1772 chargers located on opposite sides. Be sure to write a message on the "Before I Die" bucket list chalkboard while you charge up :)
